title: Ebro In The Morning -  Activist Patrisse Cullors + Jersey City Mayor Steven Fulop
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Activist Patrisse Cullors sits down with Ebro in the Morning to discuss her past work with Black Lives Matter and her current work as co-founder of the Crenshaw Dairy Mart & Jersey City Mayor Steven Fulop shows up to Ebro in the Morning to announce a competition in which the High School with the highest vaccination rate will win tickets to Summer Jam!

Along with classic Ride or Die and Curved segments hand picked by the Executive Producer of Ebro In the Morning.

Please subscribe and share the Ebro In The Morning Podcast!
